\begin_layout Standard
Welcome to Openflex Boardview (from hereon referred to simply as OFBV).
 OFBV is an advance development fork of OpenBoardView (OBV) by Chloridite
 in May 2016 as a response to seeing a need for an Open Source board viewing
 software to assist in the repairs of many electronics systems.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
At the time of writing, OFBV supports brd, bdv, asc, fz (with correct key)
 and bv (with converter to bvr) board formats and is available on Windows
 (7 onwards), OSX and Linux.
\end_layout

