<cell alignment="left" valignment="top" topline="true" leftline="true" rightline="true" usebox="none">
\begin_inset Text

\begin_layout Plain Layout
Very common board format, detected by the presence of strings such as 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

dd:1.3" 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

<<format.asc>>" and "<<pins.asc>>" in the content.
